column2: ggplot(df, aes(x = work_type)) + geom_bar(stat = "count", fill = "red") + geom_text(aes(label = ..count..), stat = "count", vjust = 1.5, color = "white") + ggtitle("Distribution of Patients type of work") + theme_classic() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1))
